B.Au=new A.e9("Mobile Technical Lead","Ciklum","january 2017","april 2018","While still acting as a cross-platform mobile developer, I had more administrative activities.",B.D7)
B.Ec=A.b(s(["I developed cross-platform mobile applications in C#. Worked with F#, Objective-C, Swift, and Java. My target OS were iOS, Android, WP7, WP8, and UWP (Windows 10). Frameworks I used: Xamarin, Xamarin.Forms, FreshMvvm, Reactive Extensions, ReactiveProperty, RxUI, MvvmCross. I worked via TDD using NUnit, MSTest, and Moq. For a few projects used BDD with Calabash and Ruby. I acted as the chief reviewer during code reviews.","My primary responsibilities were team coaching and technical quality assurance. I improved and automated the internal processes: CI, metrics, workflows, and other best practices. I have conducted internal and external interviews.","I made estimations, participated in workshops, project, and proposal reviews. Supervised and participated in technology investigations and researches. Consulted client-side developers, responded for high-level architecture for projects."]),t.s)
